## ðŸ“š Project Overview

This case study focuses on solving real-world business problems for **Swiggy Instamart** using SQL techniques of various complexities.

Swiggy Instamart is an instant grocery delivery service that ensures customers receive groceries and essentials quickly at their doorstep.  
Our goal is to analyze the data related to customers, products, orders, delivery partners, warehouses, and suppliers to generate actionable insights and improve business operations.

